{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/physics.gif?t=1732727468\" /><br><br><strong>Surmount</strong> is a free-flowing, physics-based platforming adventure where you\u2019ll experience the joys of mountain climbing. Make your perilous ascent through the various handcrafted and procedurally generated challenges of Mount Om, all the while following a silly story with eccentric folks along the way. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/camp.gif?t=1732727468\" /><br><br>Master your own unique style of climbing either alone or with a friend, upgrade and customize your climber to stand a better chance, and maybe just maybe, you'll be the first ever to reach the top!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675000/extras/multiplayer.gif?t=1732727468\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Procedural &amp; Handmade Levels</h2>Be the first to reach the top of Mount Om, the highest mountain in the world. Discover an endless amount of unique climbing routes along the way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Physics-Based Climbing</h2>An approachable physics-based climbing system that is endlessly replayable and not overly punishing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meet eccentric characters</h2>On your way to the top of Mount Om, you'll meet a variety of eccentric characters. All with their own reasons to journey to the top.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Items &amp; Upgrades</h2>Unlock a variety of permanent and equipable items that will boost your stats.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customize Your Character</h2>Be the most fashionable climber out there by customizing your character's look.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Daily Mountain</h2>Test your skills and compete with your friends in the Daily Mountain challenge!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solo or Duo!</h2>Play on your own or tethered to a friend in local co-op.<br><br><br